cancelProposal(uint256).details: Cancels a proposal (only by the proposer or admin)

params.proposalId: ID of the proposal to cancel

castVote(uint256,bool).details: Casts a vote on a proposal

params.support: True for voting in favor, false for voting against

params.callData: Function call data to execute if proposal passes
params.target: Address of the contract to call

deleteExpiredProposals(uint256).details: Clean up expired proposals to save gas

params.proposalId: ID of the proposal to clean up

executeProposal(uint256).details: Executes a successful proposal after the voting period and execution delay

params.proposalId: ID of the proposal to execute

getProposalDescription(uint256).details: Gets the description of a proposal

getProposalProposer(uint256).details: Gets the proposer of a proposal

getProposalState(uint256).details: Gets the current state of a proposal

getProposalVotes(uint256).details: Gets the votes of a proposal

getVoteByUser(uint256,address).details: Gets how a specific user voted on a proposal

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setTargetWhitelist(address,bool).details: Whitelist or blacklist a target address (only owner)

params.allowed: True to whitelist, false to blacklist

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
